Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:42.87,sign_2441_7_Where_the_hell_d,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,350)}Why the hell are \Nyou so confident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:49.59,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think about it! \NDon't think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:52.13,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it gets to me, \NI can't do anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:54.84,Watamote-flashback,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a problem if you \Ndon't start taking me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.01,Watamote-flashback,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:02.54,Watamote-flashback,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:05.93,Watamote-flashback,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,You were just so cute, \NI couldn't help teasing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:09.56,Watamote-flashback,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness! You sure got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.38,Watamote-flashback,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Shima-chan, you're such a troublemaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:13.07,Watamote-flashback,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:15.78,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't count! Doesn't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:18.28,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Just some normal physical contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:21.20,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:22.78,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
