Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.42,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Huge prize for the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.46,Default,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
