Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:38.01,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the designer will sign\N and make it out to the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.78,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,It's a one-of-a-kind drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.01,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I want it so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:44.03,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,First, I've gotta consider the design...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:45.27,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
